com.layers.app.data

Class ScaleDataService

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.layers.app.data.ScaleDataService
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ScaleDataInterface

    public class ScaleDataService
extends java.lang.Object
implements ScaleDataInterface

    Data Access Object that retrieves data requested from the ScaleBusinessService. Most queries are dependent to the location the data is relevent to.

    All querys are performed in a prepared statement to protect the arguments from SQL injection. Prepared Statement queries and result sets may be assembled and parsed, respectively, using a helper function from the class this DAO is relevent to.

    See Also:
    Scale, ScaleBusinessService
